{"tid":50444,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 係下白泥走果時有對情侶行行下唔知去左邊","createTime":"2016-12-22T11:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T12:01:19.000Z","uid":13681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"49934b0aaaf9ca6761b3280e27bab9530d9b896d","tid":50444,"uid":13681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:46:06.000Z","msg":"話說今日同女朋友去下白泥坐下睇日落影下相咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  跟住日落完左就走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  成堆人係外面等 等左勁耐啲小巴全部唔接我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟住就有人拉隊去總站坐車 但天都黑曬 越行就越唔對路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但大家都係照行 越行就越驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但突然有對情侶冇啦啦停低 調頭行走左，果刻我都有懷疑會唔會成班人一齊行錯路，但最後都決定繼續行。最後就成功行到車站坐車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但問題係 岩岩果對情侶去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  架車沿路都見佢地唔到 到底佢地去左邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我依家好擔心你地，如果你地見到個post就報平安啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c5b3e77c098891cae63638f5486589972cf3187","tid":50444,"uid":44678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:46:48.000Z","msg":"無事啦我地 放心啦"},{"pid":"9a976903937cdd23e0170c17cd2d15bd1de6b8fe","tid":50444,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:46:58.000Z","msg":"可能去左打野戰姐"},{"pid":"6cca7af513e0402147a370c5b91a7c394307855a","tid":50444,"uid":25359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:48:16.000Z","msg":"睇撚到暈 小妹要小啲自慰先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18c7a8a3f087d89821b4abb8a6ca8026f41cde6","tid":50444,"u